OL,3,CNew co-leaders of Reform Jersey
OL,4,Cannounced after vote
OL,6,FDeputies Lyndsay Feltham and Montfort
OL,7,FTadier have been named co-leaders of
OL,8,FReform Jersey after they received the
OL,9,Fsame number of votes in secret poll of
OL,10,Fparty members on Thursday evening.
OL,12,FParty Chair Helen Evans confirmed that
OL,13,Fthe election would be re-run, but not
OL,14,Fbefore September, and they would not
OL,15,Fbe announcing how many members backed
OL,16,Feach candidate.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
