OL,3,CNew co-leaders of Reform Jersey
OL,4,Cannounced after vote
OL,6,FThe Annual General Meeting (AGM) also
OL,7,Fsaw members opt to start a
OL,8,Fconsultation on changing the party's
OL,9,Fname - which would distance it from
OL,10,Fbeing confused with Reform UK when
OL,11,Ftheir politicial perspectives are
OL,12,Fsignificantly different.
OL,14,FJust a day after last month's General
OL,15,FElection, which turned out to be a
OL,16,Fdifficult night for the island's
OL,17,Flargest party, Deputy Tadier told ITV
OL,18,FNews that a rebrand might be necessary.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
