PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783797589
OL,3,CNew co-leaders of Reform Jersey
OL,4,Cannounced after vote
OL,6,FOutgoing Leader Sam Mezec lost his
OL,7,Fseat after failing in his bid to
OL,8,Fbecome a Senator, having first served
OL,9,Fas a Deputy in 2014 when he was just
OL,10,F23.
OL,12,FAnother prominent party voice, then
OL,13,FEducation Minister Rob Ward, missed
OL,14,Fout in the race for Constable of St
OL,15,FHelier.
OL,17,FIn the meantime, Deputy Feltham has
OL,18,Fbeen the Interim Leader and will now
OL,19,Fsplit the role with Deputy Tadier.
OL,26,@nD@Vrr
