OL,3,CNew co-leaders of Reform Jersey
OL,4,Cannounced after vote
OL,6,FReform Jersey describes itself as a
OL,7,Fsocial democratic party, highlighting
OL,8,F"that it is the duty of the state, in
OL,9,Fpartnership with its citizens, to help
OL,10,Fcreate a society that works for all,
OL,11,Fincluding the poorest and most
OL,12,Fdisadvantaged".
OL,14,FFormed as a pressure group in 2012 to
OL,15,Fcampaign for electoral reform, it
OL,16,Fofficially registered as a political
OL,17,Fparty in 2014 to compete in that
OL,18,Fyear's General Election.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
