OL,3,CNew co-leaders of Reform Jersey
OL,4,Cannounced after vote
OL,6,FDeputy Tadier is a founding member of
OL,7,FReform Jersey. He was brought up in St
OL,8,FBrelade and was first elected there in
OL,9,F2008.
OL,11,FHe has won re-election five times
OL,12,Fsince then and has served as Assistant
OL,13,FMinister across various departments.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Deputy Feltham has been
OL,16,FReform's Deputy Leader since 2023 and
OL,17,Fwas the party's chairperson between
OL,18,F2019 and 2022.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
