OL,3,CNew co-leaders of Reform Jersey
OL,4,Cannounced after vote
OL,6,FShe was first elected as Deputy of St
OL,7,FHelier Central in 2022 and served as
OL,8,FSocial Security Minister for part of
OL,9,Fthe last Assembly.
